    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. It has been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no spills, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. If you want that brand-new feeling without the brand-new price tag, this is your lucky day! Come grab it before someone else does!",
