    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This pristine vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled garage and maintained with an open checkbook. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the original factory scent still lingers. Every button, switch, and feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. Mechanically, the car is flawless, accompanied by a comprehensive binder of service records from a certified specialist. With exceptionally low mileage and a single-owner history, this is arguably the finest example currently on the market. It drives tight, shifts smoothly, and offers a level of refinement that must be experienced in person.",
      "price": 48500.0,
